const v1 = '/api/v1';
const FOOTPRINTS_API = {
  LOGIN: `${v1}/login/`,
  PASSWORD_RESET: `${v1}/password-reset/`,
  FORGOT_PASSWORD: `${v1}/forgot-password/`,
  CHANGE_PASSWORD: `${v1}/password-change/`,
  PASSWORD_RESET_VERIFY_TOKEN: `${v1}/token-verification/`,
  USER: `${v1}/user/`,
  ORG_UNITS: `${v1}/units/`,
  DEPARTMENTS: `${v1}/department/`,
  ORG_UNITS_DETAILS: `${v1}/unit/:orgUnitId/`,
  ASSET_ATTRIBUTES: `${v1}/attributes/`,
  ASSET_TYPES: `${v1}/asset/types/`,
  BREADCRUMBS: `${v1}/unit/:id/parents/`,
  ASSET_ATTRIBUTES_DETAILS: `${v1}/attributes/:assetAttrId/`,
  ASSET_TYPES_DETAILS: `${v1}/asset/types/:assetTypeId/`,
  ORG_UNIT_ALL: `${v1}/units/all/`,
  UPDATE_USER: `${v1}/user/:userId/`,
  UPDATE_ORG_UNIT: `${v1}/unit/:orgUnitId/`,
  ASSETS_LIST: `${v1}/assets/`,
  ASSET_DETAILS: `${v1}/asset/:assetId`,
  TRACKING_LOGS: `${v1}/tracking/logs/`,
  UPDATE_ASSET_TYPE: `${v1}/asset/types/:assetTypeId/`,
  UPDATE_ASSET_ATTRIBUTE: `${v1}/attributes/:assetAttrId/`
};

export { v1, FOOTPRINTS_API };
